# Role Access System - Sentrina

Ang Sentrina Property Management System ay may built-in na Role-Based Access Control (RBAC).

## Mga User Roles

### 1. Admin (System Administrator)
- Full access sa lahat ng features
- Database table: admins
- Makakita ng Audit Logs

### 2. Staff
- Limited administrative access
- Database table: staffs
- Hindi makakita ng Audit Logs

### 3. Resident/User (Homeowner)
- Basic user access
- Database table: residents
- Sariling data lang makikita

## Menu Access per Role

| Feature      | Admin | Staff | Resident |
|--------------|-------|-------|----------|
| Dashboard    |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ✅    |
| GIS Map      |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ✅    |
| Residents    |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ❌    |
| Payments     |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ❌    |
| Billing      |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ✅    |
| Violations   |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ✅    |
| Reports      |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ❌    |
| Audit Logs   |   ✅  |   ❌  |    ❌    |
| Notification |   ❌  |   ❌  |    ✅    |
| Payment      |   ❌  |   ✅  |    ✅    |
| Profile      |   ✅  |   ✅  |    ✅    |

