## Key Files

- server/routes/auth.js - Login/Register/Logout logic
- src/App.jsx - Route handling based on role
- src/backend/config/create-tables.js - Database schema
- src/frontend/pages/admin/components/Sidebar.jsx - Admin menu
- src/frontend/pages/staff/components/Sidebar.jsx - Staff menu
- src/frontend/pages/user/components/Sidebar.jsx - User menu